WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:04.000
The climate of Abu Dhabi is hot and arid

00:05.000 --> 00:08.000
In the summer, temperatures average above 35 degrees Celsius and humidity is high

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
In the winter, average temperatures range between 18 and 25 degrees Celsius

00:13.000 --> 00:16.000
There is very little rainfall, as it is a desert

